<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Execute a Successful and Ethical Marketing Campaign</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="joint">Executing a successful marketing campaign will help you generate a substantial amount of exposure for your products</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1002" relname="joint">and also portray your business in a positive light .</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1003" relname="joint">A successful marketing campaign will also translate into stronger sales .</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="1007" relname="span">As with any area of life , ethics is one of the things</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="5" relname="elaboration">that you have to take seriously</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1007" relname="circumstance">when creating an advertising campaign .</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="1003" relname="joint">While taking shortcuts may be advantageous</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1003" relname="joint">in speeding up the process ,</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1003" relname="joint">sometimes they may work against you .</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="1011" relname="preparation">The following five tips will help you run a successful and entirely ethical marketing campaign .</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="1012" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1013" relname="preparation">Strive for high-quality content .</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="15" relname="attribution">Your advertising should clearly state</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="1014" relname="span">how your product or service are different from others .</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1016" relname="same_unit">This is true</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="1016" relname="same_unit">whether you employ videos , images or text .</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1018" relname="span">Do not present a simplistic explanation of the products</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="18" relname="elaboration">you are offering .</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="1020" relname="sequence">Use a descriptive approach ,</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="1021" relname="span">and provide a link</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="21" relname="elaboration">to where customers can make purchases .</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1013" relname="joint">The content should catch the attention of the audience</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1013" relname="joint">and motivate them to take action .</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="1013" relname="joint">Insist on honesty .</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="27" relname="circumstance">When sharing your story with the public ,</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="1026" relname="span">make sure your ads tell the truth .</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="1028" relname="concession">While being less than truthful about your products or services may possibly help you get ahead in the short-term ,</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1029" relname="span">there is always a chance</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="29" relname="elaboration">that it will come back to bite you in the future .</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1032" relname="condition">If something like that happens ,</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1032" relname="joint">it will ruin your credibility</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1032" relname="joint">and make it hard for people to believe you ever again .</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="1028" relname="joint">Do not misrepresent facts .</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1036" relname="circumstance">As with outright lying ,</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1037" relname="span">you may feel like distorting facts</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="36" relname="purpose">to improve your image ,</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="1036" relname="contrast">but that may work against you in the long run .</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1040" relname="span">When you twist facts</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="39" relname="purpose">to suit your needs ,</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="1041" relname="joint">you risk destroying not only your credibility</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="1042" relname="span">but also the credibility of the media outlet</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="42" relname="elaboration">carrying your campaign .</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1044" relname="span">You will also be deceiving the public</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="44" relname="means">by providing them with incorrect information .</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="1028" relname="joint">Do not slander your competitors .</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="1047" relname="span">It 's natural to want to represent your products</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="47" relname="purpose">as being better than theirs ,</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1049" relname="span">but you should do it the right way</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="49" relname="means">by actually providing a superior product or service .</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="52" relname="condition">If your product/service is not superior in any way ,</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="1051" relname="span">you should strive to make it so .</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="1054" relname="span">It is valid to present a distinction for the sake</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="53" relname="elaboration">of comparing your products with someone else 's ,</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="1053" relname="span">but do n't sound " whiny " or defensive about it .</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="57" relname="condition">If you criticize a competitor ,</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1056" relname="span">it never looks good .</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="1028" relname="joint">It just reflects poorly on your own character .</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="1028" relname="joint">Avoid offering bribes for press coverage .</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1061" relname="span">Even though you may really want a reporter or producer to cover a launch event for the products and services</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="60" relname="elaboration">that you are offering ,</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="1062" relname="span">it is a bad idea to bribe them</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="62" relname="purpose">in order to make that happen .</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1064" relname="joint">Doing that makes you look desperate ,</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="1064" relname="joint">and it also makes your story less worthy of exposure .</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="67" relname="condition">If the reporter even considers taking a bribe ,</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="1065" relname="span">he/she risks getting fired .</segment>
